title: Local Hour: Greg Cote's Health Scare
description:
Le Batard, Stugotz, Greg Cote and the crew react to the Dolphins beating the Bills on Sunday and Billy wants to know who is in and who is out on the Dolphins. Also, we discuss the Cesta Cyclones opening match on Friday night and the serious health scare that happened to Greg Cote.
